      • decrementBalance

        private void decrementBalance(AVLTree.AVLNode<E> node)
        Method to decrement the balance field and to reset the value of increase. node The AVL node whose balance is to be decremented The balance field was correct prior to an insertion [or removal,] and an item is either been added to the left[ or removed from the right]. The balance is decremented and the increase flags is set to false if the overall height of this subtree has not changed.

      • incrementBalance

        private void incrementBalance(AVLTree.AVLNode<E> node)
        Method to increment the balance field and to reset the value of increase. node The AVL node whose balance is to be incremented The balance field was correct prior to an insertion [or removal,] and an item is either been added to the right[ or removed from the left]. The balance is incremented and the increase flags is set to false if the overall height of this subtree has not changed.
